Bowtie 2 authors
Primary contact <blangmea@jhsph.edu>

Ben Langmead wrote Bowtie 2, based partially on Bowtie which was written
by Ben Langmead and Cole Trapnell.  A DLL from the pthreads for Win32
library is distributed with the Win32 version of Bowtie 2.  The pthreads
for Win32 library and the GnuWin32 package have many contributors (see
their respective web sites).

Various users have kindly supplied patches, bug reports and feature
requests over the years.  Many, many thanks go to them.

Websites:

 Bowtie & Bowtie 2:  http://bowtie-bio.sf.net
 pthreads for Win32: http://sourceware.org/pthreads-win32
 GnuWin32:           http://gnuwin32.sf.net

March 2011
